OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening to come and often very windy,
OL,7,Fparticularly around coasts with a risk
OL,8,Fof gales. Spells of rain becoming more
OL,9,Fwidespread through the early hours.
OL,10,FStaying mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FAn unsettled start to the week
OL,13,Fwith wind and rain though some drier
OL,14,Fspells to end the day with lighter
OL,15,Fwinds. Temperatures remain above
OL,16,Faverage for the time of year.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
