OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDrier
OL,6,Foverall on Tuesday and Wednesday with
OL,7,Fhigh pressure in charge. A chance of
OL,8,Frain returning on Thursday. Staying
OL,9,Fmild with winds easing.
